itl.enabler.api.types

  • Packages that use itl.enabler.api.types 
    Package Description
    itl.enabler.api
    The core forecourt classes needed by your application to connect to the Enabler
    itl.enabler.api.events.forecourt
    Contains classes needed for handling forecourt events
    itl.enabler.api.types
    Contains classes representing variants of different forecourt objects

    ReservedType

    TransactionClearTypes
    Transaction clear type
    UnitOfMeasure
